<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3707418>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A) Holotype (MZFC 33964), and B) paratype (MZFC 8024) of Eleutherodactylus erythrochomus in life." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3707418/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3707420>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A) Details of hand, and B) feet of the holotype of Eleutherodactylus erythrochomus (MZFC 33964). Scale bar = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3707420/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3707422>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. General habitat of Eleutherodactylus erythrochomus sp. nov. in Palo Gordo, Guerrero;A) view of the habitat during the rainy season, B) and dry season; C) microhabitats formed by piles of large granitic boulders covered by vegetation; and D) shows the change of landscape for agricultural purposes, this is common in several localities of the region." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3707422/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

